{
  "stem": "14737.2",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And at that time, they gave our orders on the radio with a lot of brochures that Jews shouldn't get out from their houses, should remain confined to their houses.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We didn't know what the reason, but assumed-- actually, it was suppose Hitler was supposed to come to Brno to the [? second ?].",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He was in Prague.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And Hitler came there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I, being considered myself, I'm not a citizen there any longer.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I'm [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Who's going to tell me I'm a Jew, not a Jew?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I'm in the street like another.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I went out and was a big parade.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "If it's true that it was Hitler-- some people say it may not be-- then I've seen Hitler at that time.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This was on a Friday, March the 17th, on a parade, from far away, naturally, in a car.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Some say it may not have been Hitler, maybe some image.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But this history will prove much more.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Jews were confined.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And Jews were hiding in the houses.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Most Jews were wealthy Jews, so they had houses.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They had business.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "From that day on, every day started demonstrations, all kind.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Now Jews are not allowed to go to doctors, to non-Jews.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Jews are not supposed to have-- and so on.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "These stories, I'm not going to repeat here.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "History has all this.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "What am I doing--",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was able out there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No one is going to tell me I'm a Jew.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I'm not a Jew.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I mean, [?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I had to. ?] And beside, if someone would find me, I had that I belong to Hungary, because I-- that I, I am from Dolha.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But Jews didn't go out so much.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And everyone was busy with emigration now.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Jewish stores were closed, was written down 'Jude' and every place [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
